      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available now is this driver-focused E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a high-compression ratio for razor-sharp throttle response. Mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual, this chassis remains balanced with a factory limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes a VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural integrity under high lateral loads. The suspension retains its OEM damping characteristics, offering a communicative feedback loop through the hydraulic steering rack. A mechanically sound example ready for the apex.",
